					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I didn't realize you were using 16k NROM when I posted my example. I've almost never seen someone target just 16k for a homebrew!<br /><br />For my example you would need to modify PRG to start at $C000 and be of size $4000, then modify CODE to start at $C000. If you want to use DPCM, maybe still start DPCM at $C000 and put CODE after it with no specified start so that it will just fill space between the DPCM segment and the vector table.<br /><br />Or alternatively just specify 2 PRG banks in the header instead of 1 to get a 32k NROM.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

